{
  "schema": "reasoning_router_secrets_local_v1",
  "contract_version": 1,
  "_note": "``OPENAI_API_KEY`` in the process environment wins. If unset, the adapter (once per process) reads a host file: default ``~/.blackbox_secrets/openai.env`` (``chmod 600``; dir ``~/.blackbox_secrets`` mode 700), or override with ``BLACKBOX_OPENAI_ENV_FILE``. Lines: ``export OPENAI_API_KEY='...'`` or ``OPENAI_API_KEY=...``. No key in the repo. This JSON is not read. For systemd, prefer ``EnvironmentFile=`` with ``KEY=value`` lines."
}
